title: First Aid Usmle Step 1 2014 android app
description:
First Aid USMLE Step 1 2014 v1.0 

Developed by Usatine Media, LLC 

This interactive app is based on the full content of First Aid for the USMLE Step 1, 2014 by McGraw-Hill. 

Requirements: 2.2 and Up
Overview: The world's bestselling medical review book, with more than 1,250 frequently tested facts and mnemonics. This app runs fast and is designed to be user-friendly for your mobile device. There is also an interactive Q&A mode based on the Rapid Review section of the book.
